  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/e8be5e8290870e748ec3369acb67b1c1.avif?t=1753410576\" width=610 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/73204f08ecddea672e3694c9207f6fab.poster.avif?t=1753410576\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/73204f08ecddea672e3694c9207f6fab.webm?t=1753410576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/73204f08ecddea672e3694c9207f6fab.mp4?t=1753410576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Grid-based and turn-based roguelike[/h2]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After defeat in the war against the Udtmos, we were forced to flee the stellar system.<br>We must rewind everything with only three pilots.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/33db652f05f496e6e5d70c480c3ccdb7.webp?t=1753410576\" width=353 height=48 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/d35d2736550abb445021b7698a888069.poster.avif?t=1753410576\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/d35d2736550abb445021b7698a888069.webm?t=1753410576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/d35d2736550abb445021b7698a888069.mp4?t=1753410576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Create the ultimate ship</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Various Reactor Cores</strong> - You will obtain a Reactor Core at the end of each battle that you can mount on your ship. And its effect will stack with each other.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Various ships and weapons</strong> - All ships have two weapons with different effects. And you can craft and equip a sub weapon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/fff4160301297bed32775db6760a230a.poster.avif?t=1753410576\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/fff4160301297bed32775db6760a230a.webm?t=1753410576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/fff4160301297bed32775db6760a230a.mp4?t=1753410576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Reach the star through the best path</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Various missions</strong> - On the battlefield, you'll encounter various missions, such as destroying incubators or blocking portals. And maybe even some random events in the Dark Zone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Various bosses</strong> - The higher Udtmos that defend the planet each have special abilities. Unpredictable boss battles will require your best strategic choices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/d03b9cb0e0b105a3c3b5b79663ca41fd.poster.avif?t=1753410576\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/d03b9cb0e0b105a3c3b5b79663ca41fd.webm?t=1753410576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/d03b9cb0e0b105a3c3b5b79663ca41fd.mp4?t=1753410576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>There's more</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Turn Rewind</strong> - Once per battle, you can return all ally ships to the state at the beginning of the turn. You can fire ships' weapons or move ships 2 times.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Carrier</strong> - The carrier has no combat abilities, but due to its Temporal Rewinder, you must defend it and fight no matter what.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Various Carrier Skills and Enhancers</strong> - You can also craft Carrier Skills and Enhancers that can be useful in battle. Rescuing and placing survivors can also unlock additional abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >We're looking forward to your victory.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/49be7608f1658a5f6c590a6bba75ff49.poster.avif?t=1753410576\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/49be7608f1658a5f6c590a6bba75ff49.webm?t=1753410576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/49be7608f1658a5f6c590a6bba75ff49.mp4?t=1753410576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
